    SDA is the serial data
    SCL is the serial clock

    GND --> GND
    VCC --> 5V
    SDA --> A4
    SCL --> A5
  -------------------------------
  DISPLAY - I2C
    SDA is the serial data
    SCL is the serial clock
      
  -------------------------------
  RTC-DS3231 - I2C
    SDA is the serial data
    SCL is the serial clock
      
  -------------------------------
  RELAY
    D5  --> Relay1
    D6  --> Relay2
    D7  --> Relay3
    D8  --> Relay4
  -------------------------------

*/
